Jean Poiret https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Poiret 0 Jean Poiret, born Jean Poiré, (17 August 1926 in Paris – 14 March 1992) was a French actor, director, and screenwriter. He is primarily known as the author of the original play La Cage Aux Folles.
